"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-01-Olympic-Medals-From-Gold-to-Green--1vIrS9t0mtO-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  It's now common knowledge that Olympic gold medals are not pure gold, but Paris 2024 is upping the game: All 5,084 medals feature a piece of the Eiffel Tower at their center. This creative touch not only emphasizes a commitment to sustainability but also celebrates the city's iconic symbol. From recycled car parts in Rio to e-waste in Tokyo, the Games is blending sports with eco-friendly innovation.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"